2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong: MLML 204:Exper & Sampl Design-  Basic design of experiments and field sampling, including random and systematic sampling, subsampling, survey techniques, single and multifactor experiments using randomized, nested, and blocked experimental designs, and data analyses. Offered through Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML); contact SEP program office for MLML registration procedures.
